summary.label:
Stickr allows you to create, export and share your own stickers.

Name a sticker pack and create stickers with one of our 4 different modalities:

- Auto Cut technology from your photo gallery to select the subject you want to create the sicker of, then share it with Stickr App;
- Copy from subject from Safari, then share it with Stickr App;
- Free hand from Stickr App;
- Smart Selection from Stickr App.

Easily export the sticker pack to WhatsApp, iMessage or Telegram.

Finally, you can share your creations with your friends.

This app gives you the possibility to create an unlimited number of packs and to own the best sticker library on your phone so that you can quickly share as many stickers as you wish!
